Milestone plan written at the start of 2003

Milestone 0 (by second half April)
-----------
 o Minimal Interface Builder
 o No function for saving
 o No interaction with animator

Milestone 1 (by second half May)
-----------
 o Minimal Interface Builder
 o Able to save interfaces
 o No interaction with animator

Milestone 2 (by first half July)
-----------
 o Minimal Interface Builder
 o Able to save interfaces
 o Interacts with animator

Milestone 3 (by second half July)
-----------
 o Minimal Interface Builder & Animator
 o With animation history

Milestone 4 (by second half August)
-----------
 o Interface Builder & Animator with history
 o Simple interface generator (from ZML)

Milestone 5 (by second half September)
-----------
 o Interface Builder & Animator with history
 o Improved interface generator (from ZML) (?)

Milestone 6 (by second half October)
-----------
 o Interface Builder/Animator/Generator with Animation history
 o Extra plugins

Milestone 7 (by second half November)
-----------
 o Any extra documentation needed
   * Maintainer
   * Plugin developer
   * User



